Business class standard dropped  Took SQ business class from Singapore to Istanbul, it’s quite shocking that the standard has dropped significantly: 
1) the seat was not cleaned properly, and the remote control had food stains on it; 
2) the wifi that showed it’s connected didn’t work at all, the aircrews attempted to fix the problem but no success; 
3) the in-flight entertainment suddenly switched off by itself and unable to restart while I was half way watching a show; 
4) the washroom run out of tissue paper; and what made it worse was 
5) while waiting for my turn outside the lavatory, the Pilot came out and cut my queue! I understand that the crews may have priorities as they are on duty, but he was simply rude!
